at the WMAP 7-year data are consistent with Gaussian primordial fluctuations\nwithin ~2{\\sigma} CL. We stress however the importance of taking into account\nthe unresolved point sources in the measurement of fnl in future works,\nespecially when using more precise data sets such as the forthcoming Planck\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 May 2011 20:15:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2011 11:35:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
