 six brown dwarfs are\nhighly metal rich relative to the Sun if the recent solar C & O abundances are\ncorrect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 31 May 2011 14:41:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
